sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid parallel fragments
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid par and and fragments mapped onto sequencer fragment branches.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/10-parallel/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/10-parallel
}
participant Caller
participant Service
participant DB
participant Audit
par Primary branch [Mermaid: par Primary branch]
  Caller->>Service: Begin primary work [Mermaid: Caller->>Service: Begin primary work]
and Database branch [Mermaid: and Database branch]
  Service->>DB: Persist data [Mermaid: Service->>DB: Persist data]
and Audit branch [Mermaid: and Audit branch]
  opt Optional audit [Mermaid: opt Optional audit]
    Service->>Audit: Emit audit event [Mermaid: Service->>Audit: Emit audit event]
  end
end
